{"tid":1694769,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"消息：受傷科大生情況相當差　未到腦幹死亡測試階段","createTime":"2019-11-05T09:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T09:36:02.000Z","uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eb12a09bf8e12249901baecf801c8e51f68f5d75","tid":1694769,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:36:02.000Z","msg":"星期日晚在將軍澳尚德邨停車場，懷疑由3樓跌落2樓重傷的科大學生，情況仍然危殆。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">據了解，他仍未去到要做腦幹死亡測試的階段</span>，但情況相當差，消息指，傷者已接受了兩次手術，包括切除了部分腦組織，以降低腦壓。<br />\n<br />\n一批防暴警察星期日晚深夜至翌日凌晨，在將軍澳尚德邨和廣明苑外，發射多輪催淚彈驅散堵路的人，期間一名科大生懷疑躲避警方的催淚彈期間 ，由尚德邨停車場3樓跌落2樓  ，目前在伊利沙伯醫院深切治療部治療。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1490202-20191105.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1490202-20191105.htm&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwHocbXMCqCW%2BK0Nx6tfHLyc%3D&h=cc7fa59f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1490202-20191105.htm&h=578a326a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1490202-20191105.htm</a><br />\n<br />\nRTHK <a href=\"http://點都準過on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E9%BB%9E%E9%83%BD%E6%BA%96%E9%81%8Eon.cc&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwHocbXMCqCW%2BK0Nx6tfHLyc%3D&h=d261ff39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">點都準過on.cc</a> 同乜01 掛~~~<br />\n<br />\n撐住呀周同學~<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}